What is Identifer? Name in Java program
class name, method name, variable name 

Identifer Rules
---------------
1.Identifer should contains only: a to z, 0-9,$,_
2.Idetifier should start with digits  o to 9
3.Identifer should not contains any special char/symbol
4.Should not use,keyword/RS has identifers.
5.Identifers case senstive

